\begin_layout Standard
However, the value chain they focus on seems to be missing an important
 link.
 For many commodities, farmers will sell at the farm gate to a trader, who
 will then aggregate production and link further to processors.
 It is likely that especially farmers that sell only small quantities will
 rely on traders.
 As such, an exclusive focus on the farmer-processor link may mean findings
 are affected by selection bias.
\end_layout

